## JACOCO SETUP — VERIFY IN POM.XML
========================================================

If jacoco plugin is missing from pom.xml, add it:

  <plugin>
      <groupId>org.jacoco</groupId>
      <artifactId>jacoco-maven-plugin</artifactId>
      <version>0.8.11</version>
      <executions>
          <execution>
              <id>prepare-agent</id>
              <goals><goal>prepare-agent</goal></goals>
          </execution>
          <execution>
              <id>report</id>
              <phase>test</phase>
              <goals><goal>report</goal></goals>
          </execution>
          <execution>
              <id>check</id>
              <goals><goal>check</goal></goals>
              <configuration>
                  <rules>
                      <rule>
                          <limits>
                              <limit>
                                  <counter>LINE</counter>
                                  <minimum>0.90</minimum>
                              </limit>
                          </limits>
                      </rule>
                  </rules>
              </configuration>
          </execution>
      </executions>
  </plugin>

Also add this to pom.xml to read CSV report easily:
  The jacoco.csv file is at: target/site/jacoco/jacoco.csv
  Format: GROUP,PACKAGE,CLASS,INSTRUCTION_MISSED,...,LINE_MISSED,LINE_COVERED,...

========================================================
## READING JACOCO CSV (critical for loop logic)
========================================================

After every test run, read target/site/jacoco/jacoco.csv

CSV columns are:
  GROUP, PACKAGE, CLASS,
  INSTRUCTION_MISSED, INSTRUCTION_COVERED,
  BRANCH_MISSED, BRANCH_COVERED,
  LINE_MISSED, LINE_COVERED,
  COMPLEXITY_MISSED, COMPLEXITY_COVERED,
  METHOD_MISSED, METHOD_COVERED

Calculate coverage per class:
  LINE_COVERAGE = LINE_COVERED / (LINE_MISSED + LINE_COVERED) * 100

Calculate overall coverage:
  TOTAL_COVERED = sum of all LINE_COVERED
  TOTAL_MISSED  = sum of all LINE_MISSED
  OVERALL = TOTAL_COVERED / (TOTAL_COVERED + TOTAL_MISSED) * 100

Classes below 90%:
  Filter rows where LINE_COVERAGE < 90

